Golisano Hall.name: Golisano Hall
Golisano Hall.desription: A center for cutting-edge study and research, this building is the home to the B. Thomas Golisano College of Computing and Information Sciences. This facility includes academic classrooms and labs for computer science, information technology, and software engineering students, as well as a 151-seat auditorium and a beautiful three-story atrium.
